Spinlock Implemenattion
1)Thread Spinlock defination
2)Spinlock Statuses
3)Spin Members Handling [Global defination]
    set_owner
    get_owner
    acuire_lock
    release_lock

    spin_init 
    spin_alloc
    spin_free
4)
threadSpin_init     -> will initialize the Spinlock
threadSpin_lock     -> will acquire the Spinlock
threadSpin_trylock  -> Tries to acquire lock
threadSpin_unlock   -> will release the Spinlock
threadSpin_destroy  -> will destroy spinlock (basically will free the allocated memory for spinlock object)
